[
  {
    "type": "h1",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "How to grant permissions to functions",
        "fontSize": "20pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "center"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Permissions can be set for each function, determining what actions users with a given function can take within the system.",
        "fontSize": "12pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Configuring permissions allows you to grant certain users access and restrict others based on their function.",
        "fontSize": "12pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "When the company is first registered on Tonnus, by default, the owner has all permissions, and no one else has any. The owner then grants permissions to other functions in the company.",
        "fontSize": "12pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Granting permissions",
        "fontSize": "12pt",
        "bold": "true"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "ol",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "li",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "lic",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Go to the Org Chart module.",
                "fontSize": "12pt"
              }
            ],
            "align": "justify"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/vw0NmlSoiSFDGIr4QcUrJZf3HntJEo9Fg6F497UFXbDVAxHGG-yftaohzMYIAnHaI5kL3bl-CsxucLMxqjs6CTvuYAiT9tLW7l1z5b3Ia0sy_87ShrUbYUKm0Fs-adKcMSds6VZwYjz_0irNVVbvow__EwJogt4lp-WbTukWYJwSer9yJGoAXYymYLaseQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "",
            "fontSize": "12pt"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "  2. Press on the function you want to configure permissions for: for example, HR Department.",
        "fontSize": "12pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/F6LhikwsYUzKiqkTnb3mUxlpheTZa_CyhwRGpXTEogjDAum1uHm6CV4dDLc1X8IPKRbLnBtbdSLB2__0XhnDAksvNHDaGX6ACag21nuHvOQ00YZxbRSfqVKteoKaXMgqpIz3RWmAdeaakNTBfvAozzxJlp5qun_x_0llAanEUbU01G4FpmQ5O04Kio0jnA",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "",
            "fontSize": "12pt"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "   3. In the function management panel that appears, go to the PERMISSIONS tab.",
        "fontSize": "12pt"
      }
    ],
    "align": "justify"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
